snippet.title: amberlynn reid is... something else...
snippet.description:
So if you’ve never heard of Amberlynn Reid you should count yourself lucky. Our queen Amberlynnstarted as a weight loss channel almost a decade ago and well… you tell me how that’s going. Nowadays, Amberlynn Reid no longer identifies her channel as a weight loss one but she’s more of a daily vlogger -- but you’d be wrong to think she’s out here shooting some David Dobrik style wild ass vlogs. Unlike everyone else, Amberlynn changed up the whole vlogging game by making it super boring. Now, if you’re new to Amberlynn Reid’s channel, you’d notice how she’s always getting hate bombed and all her “fans” seem to be just reading her to filth in the comments all the time. Amberlynn Reid is such a notorious liar she made like a 20-minute video confessing to all the lies she’s said. Amberlynn Reid has lied about some serious stuff but since this isn’t a deep dive, I’ll just stick to the basic stuff but if you do want a deep dive into the history of Amberlynn Reid and the detail about all the stuff she’s done please leave a comment letting me know. Now, let me introduce you to a crucial character in our story: Becky. Ms. Becky is Amberlynn Reid’s girlfriend. Or should I say WAS -- but we’ll get into that later. So here’s the thing, Amberlynn started talking to Becky the second she broke up with her other ex, Destiny. Keep that in mind cuz it’s gonna come up. So, almost immediately, Becky and Amberlynn Reid move in together. Now, this is when we start seeing Becky be dragged down by Amber and also fall into the same bad eating habits as her. You can see how Becky gains weight over time throughout this relationship. You can also see Becky try to help Amber by telling her to eat healthier and encouraging her to exercise more but I guess Amber had more influence on Becky’s lifestyle than Becky did on Amber’s. You can also start seeing how Becky enables Amber by walking the dogs herself, by taking Amber to eat out every day, or by covering up for her when she’s caught in lies. During all this, you can also see Amber does not really appreciate just how much Becky does for her. Buttt things take a turn...
